  "texts": [
    "Given a pattern to be classified, a Fourier transform (FT) is used to calculate its virtual PDF.",
    "Each spectrum is fed to a separately trained CNN that predicts a set of phases (i), where each has a confidence associated with XRD (c XRD) or PDF (c PDF).",
    "These predictions are aggregated using a confidence-weighted sum defined by the equation shown.",
    "https://doi.org/10.1038/s41524-024-01230-9",
    "the labels (x-axis) denote the phase count in the samples on which they were obtained."
  ],
